    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835970/extras/57675fa2404d7a0e6fcbdaff27984510.avif?t=1745480935\" width=630 height=122 /></span><br><br><i>“No one knew where the construct came from, one day it just suddenly appeared. A digital entity floating in cyberspace, with big letters on its side reading: ICEwall.<br><br>The construct seemingly had no purpose and yet it contained a series of programs, ICE, designed to eliminate intruders, as if its sole purpose was to challenge us.<br><br>The other runners and I were instantly hooked, like kids spending all their money playing arcade machines.”<br><br>     -      ROTN, Console Cowboy</i><br><br><br>With ICEwall I have combined the immediate action gameplay of classic shooters, with modern roguelike game design. A game that is easy to play, but with a lot of depth and replayability.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Draft power-ups as you play<br></li><li>All abilities and powers stack together<br></li><li>Build powerful, fun and creative combos<br></li><li>Bullet hell action<br></li><li>Epic boss fights<br></li><li>Multiple player ships with different starting abilities<br></li><li>Multiple game difficulties and game modes:<br>   - Arcade Mode<br>   - Hard Mode (is really hard)<br>   - Draft, No Draft and Free Draft (perfect for hunting achievements and experimenting)<br>   - Endless Mode<br></li><li>Music that slaps!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835970/extras/074e96e9cd36ef24b957687cd0cdde9f.avif?t=1745480935\" width=630 height=122 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835970/extras/cca0fc7094bf72dd0b8ba347bb746e3a.avif?t=1745480935\" width=630 height=122 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"b